==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interlink
<hw>In`ter*link"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To link
together; to join, as one chain to another.</def>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interlink</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Interlink
<hw>In`ter*link"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An intermediate
or connecting link.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interlobar</ent>⟦br⟧
